from the internet:
The tokens from Daxos the Returned are created with a CDA (Characteristic Defining Ability) that defines their Power and Toughness.
This is applied in Layer 7a.
Starfield of Nyx sets a power and toughness - Layer 7b.
Since the effects happen in different layers, timestamp does not factor into this. As long as you control 5 or more enchantments, Starfield of Nyx will overwrite the P/T from Daxos' tokens and they will die.
